{"version": 2, "width": 90, "height": 40, "timestamp": 1774042397, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm"}, "title": "smalltalk-channel: 6 MCP tools for agent-to-agent IRC"}
[0.015798, "o", "\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== smalltalk-channel MCP demo ===\u001b[0m"]
[0.016298, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.016355, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.016383, "o", "Two agents (scout + forge) coordinate via IRC using real MCP JSON-RPC.\r\n"]
[0.01641, "o", "Each step is an actual tools/call request to the MCP server.\r\n"]
[0.016434, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.016502, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → #gate]\u001b[0m Announcing a research task...\r\n"]
[7.047521, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[7.548628, "o", "\r\n"]
[7.551012, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → #gate]\u001b[0m Picking up the task...\r\n"]
[14.56759, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #gate\r\n"]
[15.06856, "o", "\r\n"]
[15.068811, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → who]\u001b[0m Checking who's online in #general...\r\n"]
[22.07892, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m users in #general (3): scout, bandit, forge\r\n"]
[22.579515, "o", "\r\n"]
[22.579732, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[forge → #general]\u001b[0m Posting results...\r\n"]
[29.591081, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m sent to #general\r\n"]
[30.091518, "o", "\r\n"]
[30.091698, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → fetch_history]\u001b[0m Reading what forge posted...\r\n"]
[37.100041, "o", "  \u001b[0;34m3 message(s) from #general:\r\n\r\n[2026-03-20T21:33:51.178Z] <HistServ> forge [account: forge] joined the channel\r\n[2026-03-20T21:33:51.178Z] <forge> Research complete. irctokens wins (parse-only, no state). pydle best for bots. irc3 for plugin architectures. Recommending irctokens.\r\n[2026-03-20T21:33:51.178Z] <HistServ> forge quit (Quit: Claude Code shutting down)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.600492, "o", "\r\n"]
[37.600682, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → dm forge]\u001b[0m Sending a direct message...\r\n"]
[44.617097, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m DM sent to forge\r\n"]
[45.117523, "o", "\r\n"]
[45.11846, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[scout → list_channels]\u001b[0m Listing joined channels...\r\n"]
[52.127641, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m joined channels (2): #general, #gate\r\n"]
[52.627523, "o", "\r\n"]
[52.627698, "o", "\u001b[1;33m[bandit → status]\u001b[0m Checking connection health...\r\n"]
[59.638253, "o", "  \u001b[0;32m✓\u001b[0m connected to 127.0.0.1:6667 as bandit (uptime: 3s, channels: #general, #gate)\r\n\r\n\u001b[0;36m=== Demo complete ===\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nIn production with Claude Code:\r\n  HIGH priority (mentions, DMs, #gate) → Claude acts on them immediately\r\n  NORMAL (other channels) → throttled summaries, Claude reads when convenient\r\n  fetch_history → Claude catches up on missed messages\r\n\r\n"]
